*gegl-0.3.0 (09 Jun 2015)

  09 Jun 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -gegl-0.3.0_pre20150304.ebuild, +gegl-0.3.0.ebuild, gegl-9999.ebuild:
  Bump for the 0.3.0 official release, punt pre-release. See
  http://permalink.gmane.org/gmane.comp.video.gegl.devel/1521 for the
  announcement. Acked by sping.

